cine  We offer quality medical education  impact the future of medicine through advanced research and provide exceptional health care to the community through our UI Health L P  Johnson Family Health Center and other clinical endeavors  Education About Welcome From Regional Dean UIC Health Sciences Campus Rockford Fast Facts More About the Region Visiting the Campus Employment Contact Us About Education Research Patient Care Departments News Giving INFORMATION FOR  Prospective and Current Students Faculty   Staff Alumni   Friends Patients Businesses and Community RESOURCES  UIC Directory Blackboard Emergency Information Contact Us Apply Now Give Contact Us If you have questions  comments  or problems accessing this site  please E mail the webmaster College of Medicine Chicago Peoria Rockford Urbana 